it the enôÙviôÙronôÙment poses. From the gift perôÙspecôÙtive, what is hapôÙpenôÙing is that we no longer seek merely to take from the planet, but to give back as well. This corôÙreôÙsponds to the comôÙing of age of huôÙmanôÙity, tranôÙsiôÙtionôÙing from a mother-child reôÙlaôÙtionôÙship to earth, to a co-creôÙative partôÙnerôÙship in which givôÙing and reôÙceivôÙing find balôÙance.

